  <div class="registration_information">
    <ul>
      <li>How many neighbors do you know? Select the names of friends in town and we'll add them to your CommonPlace profile!</li>
      <li>Use Facebook and your email contacts to quickly find the neighbors you know:</li>
      <li class="buttons">
        <img src="/assets/buttons/facebook-connect.png" alt="Connect with Facebook" class="facebook">
        <img src="/assets/buttons/gmail-connect.png" alt="Google Connect" class="google" style="display: none">
        <img src="/assets/buttons/yahoo-connect.png" alt="Yahoo Connect" class="yahoo" style="display:none">
        <img src="/assets/buttons/hotmail-connect.png" alt="Windows Live" class="windows_live" style="display: none">
      </li>
        <li class="add">
